Now i have a job in jenkins ScientificCalculatorApp which has the pipeline script to bundle my code and push to dockerhub 
Then i use ansible to pull and create a container with that image 
Then i run the container which gives me a interface for calculator

Running jenkins Manually at Jenkins page 
To run ansible - ansible-playbook -i inventory.ini Deploy.yml
To run the container - docker run -it dharaniprasads/scientific-calculator  
